wiki.summary: “Spoil My Night” is an upbeat first collaboration between Post Malone and Swae Lee. Throughout the song, both artists detail nights filled with women and flexing their own money. Whenever women are around though, feelings seem to always interrupt a good time. The song became the fifth track that fans got to hear before "beerbongs & bentleys" was released, as Post Malone debuted it during his set at Coachella 2018. On March 13, 2019, “Spoil My Night” was certified Platinum by the RIAA. Read more on Last.fm.
